column7: How often have you been feeling sad or hopeless in the past two weeks?
column8: How often have you been feeling nervous, anxious, or on edge in the past two weeks?
column9: Have you experienced changes in your appetite or weight in the past two weeks?
column10: Have you had trouble sleeping (either difficulty falling asleep, staying asleep, or waking up too early) in the past two weeks?
column11: Have you been feeling unusually fatigued or lacking in energy in the past two weeks?
column12: Have you had trouble concentrating on things such as schoolwork or other activities in the past two weeks?
column13: Have you had recurring thoughts of death or suicide in the past two weeks?
column14: Have you experienced any physical symptoms such as racing heart, trembling, sweating, or shortness of breath without any apparent cause in the past two weeks?
column15: Have you noticed any changes in your academic performance or attendance due to emotional distress in the past two weeks?
column16: Is there anything else you would like to share about your emotional well-being or any concerns you have?
column17: Do you think you have depression or anxiety?
column18: Have you ever been diagnosed with depression or anxiety by a healthcare professional?
